column2: Howdy! I am looking for @TAMU students who are living on campus and have tested positive for COVID-19 for a story for @TheBattOnline. DM me if this is you!
Here’s a link to @TAMU’s dashboard for you to explore: https://t.co/SKXWxXC3at
NEW: Texas A&M has 1,200 confirmed cases of COVID-19 as of last Friday and tested over 30,000 campus members in August. The other ~40K are required to be tested by Sept. 10. https://t.co/GohjbsVdMZ
